4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge who aspire to become cybersecurity specialists. Through this 16-week program, students receive foundational training in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside hands-on skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The curriculum emphasizes risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Classes are conducted live online, three times a week, accommodating up to 16 students in each session. Participants are awarded an official completion certificate upon finishing the program. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop